0.22.name: wordpress/wallow
0.22.description: Multistyle theme from TwoBeers. Use one of the six default styles or mix them to get your personal one. Wallow has a lot of features, like five built-in new widgets, the quickbar (a fixed bar for your most important widgets always on top), customizable menu, background and header, widgetized sidebar.
